    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over perfection. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though you may notice some minor cosmetic wear on the interior upholstery and a few scratches and dings on the exterior paint consistent with its age. It has been regularly serviced, but the buyer should expect to address some upcoming minor maintenance items to keep it in top shape. It's a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price point.",
