    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a donor car for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running, and the transmission has significant slippage issues that make it unsafe for regular driving. Externally, there is extensive rust along the wheel arches and undercarriage, along with several large dents and peeling clear coat. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please note this car is sold strictly as-is and will need to be towed.",
