      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this incredible project opportunity! This vehicle is in poor condition and is ready for a dedicated enthusiast to bring it back to life. While it requires major mechanical and cosmetic work, it's a fantastic canvas for someone who loves a challenge and wants to build something special from the ground up!",
